      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIGHTY SCAR (1) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 4th and beaten 7 lengths at this track (29.02). Can discover winning form. FAST FREDDY (5) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (28.90) at this track behind Prison Break in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expecting another good run. JUMBUK SACHIN (2) was a course and distance placegetter (28.73) last time also from the same draw, finishing a 2.75 lengths second in a Grade 4/5. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. FANTASTIC ZOHAN (8) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
